title: Skin Deep Tattoo Magazine January 2013
description:
Skin Deep International is a sister title to Skin Shots, which is meant as a reference magazine featuring top quality tattoo work from around the globe. Also included is a Directory of many UK and International tattoo studios to help you hunt down your next masterpiece. Being a 'Pictorial' magazine, Skin deep breaks down the language barriers.
